Question: Is the hat the same color as the sign?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n571179.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='sign')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='hat')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color is the sign?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the hat?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
